item.title: Boundaries For Your Soul — with Colleen Blake-Miller
item.description: Cultivating healthy boundaries can change your life and protect your soul and well-being. In our re-release of the episode, "Boundaries For Your Soul," Allie and Colleen Blake-Miller discuss the importance of setting boundaries across various areas of life. They explore the challenges people face in establishing boundaries and provide examples of specific boundaries that can be set. They also discuss the difference between assertiveness and aggressiveness when communicating boundaries... Feed: https://rss.libsyn.com/shows/122900/destinations/724011.xml

item.title: Ep. 116: Alignment Is the New Currency for Success: Are You Spending your Energy Wisely?
item.description:
Welcome to "Thriving in Midlife Redefining Aging with Wellness" the podcast where we discuss how to live an extraordinary life in every aspect. I'm your host, Kellie Lupsha, a high-performance health coach, who is delighted to be your guide to vitality.

In this episode, I’m taking a little time to reflect with you on how we show up in our lives—our work, our family, our health, and our purpose... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/ec72da0c/podcast/rss
